OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThree men were offered payment to set
OL,8,Ffire to properties linked to Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer by a Russian-speaking contact
OL,10,Fdubbed "El Money", a court has heard.
OL,12,FRoman Lavrynovych, 22, Petro Pochynok,
OL,13,F35, and Stanislav Carpiuc, 27, are
OL,14,Fcharged with conspiracy to damage
OL,15,Fproperty by fire between April 1 and
OL,16,FMay 13 last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FLavrynovych, of Lewisham, south-east
OL,8,FLondon, is further charged with
OL,9,Fdamaging two properties by fire with
OL,10,Fintent to endanger life on May 11 and
OL,11,F12, 2025.
OL,13,FLavrynovych and Pochynok are both
OL,14,FUkrainian citizens, while Ukrainian-
OL,15,Fborn Carpiuc is a Romanian citizen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FOpening the trial at the Old Bailey on
OL,8,FWednesday, Duncan Atkinson KC said:
OL,9,F"Three fires within five days would be
OL,10,Fpretty unusual. However, three fires
OL,11,Fall involving property linked to the
OL,12,Fsame person were beyond a coincidence."
OL,14,FOn May 8, 2025, a Toyota RAV4 was
OL,15,Fdiscovered on fire in Kentish Town.
OL,16,FThe car was later discovered to have
OL,17,Fbeen previously owned by the prime
OL,18,Fminister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThree days later, on May 11, a fire
OL,8,Fwas allegedly started at the front
OL,9,Fdoor of a house converted into flats
OL,10,Fin Kentish Town in north London.
OL,12,FThe fire is alleged to have been
OL,13,Fstarted deliberately with the use of a
OL,14,Fwhite spirit being poured over the
OL,15,Ffront door. The house was managed by a
OL,16,Fcompany of which the prime minister
OL,17,Fhad once been director and shareholder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe following day, on May 12, there
OL,8,Fwas another fire at the Kentish Town
OL,9,Fhome where the prime minister had
OL,10,Flived before he moved into Downing
OL,11,FStreet after being elected.
OL,13,FThe fire had again allegedly been set
OL,14,Fdeliberately at the front door of the
OL,15,Fproperty using a white spirit.
OL,17,F"The evidence demonstrated that there
OL,18,Fwas, here, no coincidence," Mr
OL,19,FAtkinson said in his opening remarks.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"Rather, the vehicle and the two
OL,8,Fproperties in question had been
OL,9,Ftargeted, and the acts of arson at
OL,10,Fthese locations had been planned and
OL,11,Fdirected, with those involved promised
OL,12,Fpayment for their participation."
OL,14,FThe prosecution allege that
OL,15,FLavrynovych had been offered payment
OL,16,Fto set the fires by a contact using
OL,17,Fthe pseudonym 'El Money', who he was
OL,18,Fcommunicating with via Telegram.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThey had communicated in Russian,
OL,8,Fdespite Lavrynovych usually
OL,9,Fcommunicating using Ukrainian.
OL,11,FCarpiuc had also communicated with
OL,12,FLavrynovych regarding his payment. It
OL,13,Fis alleged that Pochynok was also
OL,14,Frecruited to help set the fires.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Atkinson said Lavrynovych's phone
OL,8,Fcontained location data placing it at
OL,9,Fthe location of all three fires at the
OL,10,Ftime they were set, images and videos
OL,11,Fof all three locations before fires
OL,12,Fwere set, as well as images of all
OL,13,Fthree fires, and a video showing the
OL,14,Ffire damage at the second property the
OL,15,Fnext day.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
