OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"In each case Lavrynovych set a fire
OL,8,Fat the front door of the house using
OL,9,Fwhite spirit or something similar," Mr
OL,10,FAtkinson told jurors.
OL,12,F"The fires were set in the dead of
OL,13,Fnight, when the occupants of the
OL,14,Faddresses would inevitably have been
OL,15,Fasleep.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@cO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777514612
OL,3,CRussian speaker offered men money to
OL,4,Ctarget properties linked to PM, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"The prosecution's case is that when
OL,8,Fhe did so he must have intended to
OL,9,Fendanger ` to risk ` the lives of the
OL,10,Fpeople living inside those houses. Why
OL,11,Felse would you set fire to the front
OL,12,Fdoor, blocking the residents' escape?"
OL,14,FLavrynovych, Carpiuc, from Romford,
OL,15,Feast London, and Pochynok, of
OL,16,FIslington, north London, have pleaded
OL,17,Fnot guilty to the charges against them.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
